```

## Exemplos Ãºteis
```bash
shodan search apache
shodan search port:21 country:BR
shodan search "os:Windows 7 country:BR" --fields ip_str,port,org,product,version,vulns --limit 50
shodan host IP
```

## Exportar resultado para CSV
```bash
shodan search "apache country:BR" --fields ip_str,port --limit 50 > apache_br.csv
```

## Busca por CVE
```bash
shodan search vuln:CVE-2021-26855
```
# ðŸ”¹ Buscas bÃ¡sicas
shodan search apache
shodan search nginx
shodan search port:21 country:BR
shodan search "os:Windows 7"
shodan host 201.45.132.22
